Author: ebi_chan
Text: Wow i admire your sense of responsibility!

Author: NindeNehima
Text: I understand you honey. I recently moved in with my partner and his child. I struggle with a restrict/binge cycle, but I try not to eat a ton at home then binge like crazy when they are both gone. But I want to eat enough to set a good impression for the child, and definitely NOT show her that this is a way to live.
